name: axios
text: Trump aide Ja'Ron Smith, the highest-ranking Black official in the White House: "In the wake of the murder of Breonna Taylor, George Floyd, and LeGend Taliferro — a moment of national racial consciousness — I have seen his true conscience." https://t.co/lfNacWJICu

name: axios
text:
Trump will officially accept the Republican nomination for president before a crowd of more than 1,000 people on the White House South Lawn tonight. Meanwhile, demonstrators gathered outside in Lafayette Park to protest his administration.

https://t.co/5fGtPK9Sto

name: axios
text:
IN PHOTOS: Trump will accept the GOP nomination for president in a speech tonight from the White House.

The audience of 1,000 guests is inches, not feet, apart and most are without masks.
https://t.co/R45s10BdkU
